            }
          ]
        },
        "part_type": "Hadith",
        "path": "/books/al-kafi:7:3:19:3",
        "text": [
          " سَأَلْتُ أَبَا عَبْدِ اللَّهِ ( عليه السلام ) عَنِ الزَّانِي إِذَا زَنَى أَ يُنْفَى قَالَ فَقَالَ نَعَمْ مِنَ الَّتِي جُلِدَ فِيهَا إِلَى غَيْرِهَا ."
        ],
        "translations": {
          "en.hubeali": [
            "Yunus, from Ibn Muskan, from Abu Baseer who said, ",
            "‘I asked Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> about the adulterer when he commits adultery, should he be exiled?’ So he<sup>asws</sup> said: ‘Yes, from (the city) in which he was whipped to other than it’."
          ]
        }
      },
