        "part_type": "Hadith",
        "path": "/books/al-kafi:7:3:19:4",
        "text": [
          " سَأَلْتُهُ عَنِ الزَّانِي إِذَا جُلِدَ الْحَدَّ قَالَ يُنْفَى مِنَ الْأَرْضِ إِلَى بَلْدَةٍ يَكُونُ فِيهَا سَنَةً ."
        ],
        "translations": {
          "en.hubeali": [
            "A number of our companions, from Sahl Bin Ziyad, from Ibn Abu Najran, from Musny Al Hanaat, ",
            "(The narrator) says, ‘I asked Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> about the adulterer when he is whipped the Penalty (<span class=\"iTxt\">Hadd</span>)’. He<sup>asws</sup> said: ‘He should be exiled from the land to a city to happen to be there for a year’."
          ]
        }
      }
